5D72A46F.Line1.EDC7E: We have been buried alive for weeks. Whatever collapsed the entry tunnel continues to circle us, shaking the walls as it passes again and again.

915B9773.Line5.EDC7E: Our instructors keep the creature at bay, but their powers fade every day...while Headmaster Tetharat remains locked in the restricted archive.

F7671DF1.Line3.EDC7E: The other students say it is a demon wyrm, sent by the Vizjerei to destroy us, but no one truly knows.
